RockEncantech Store

Full-stack e-commerce catalog built with Laravel (API) and React (frontend).

🚀 Features

Product listing with pagination

Search and category filter

Product details page

User registration and login

Token authentication (Laravel Sanctum)

Protected API routes

Clean architecture (Service + Repository)

🏗️ Project Structure
RockEncantech/
├── backend/
├── frontend/
├── docker-compose.yml
└── README.md

🐳 Run with Docker (Recommended)
Requirements

Docker installed

Run
docker compose up --build
🌐 Access

Frontend: http://localhost:5173

Backend: http://localhost:8000

⚙️ Automatic Setup

When running Docker, the project will:

Start MySQL

Configure environment

Run migrations and seed

Start backend and frontend

💻 Run Without Docker
Backend
cd backend

composer install
cp .env.example .env
php artisan key:generate
php artisan migrate --seed
php artisan serve
Frontend
cd frontend

npm install
npm run dev
🔐 Authentication

Token stored in localStorage

Sent via:

Authorization: Bearer {token}
📡 Main Endpoints

GET /api/products

GET /api/products/{id}

POST /api/products/{id}

DELETE /api/products/{id}

GET /api/categories

POST /api/register

POST /api/login

